document_data.History:
In the 1370s DR, Myrkyssa sought multiple times to conquer or seize control of the city of Ravens Bluff and thus exploit the wild mythal to aid her future conquests.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|137}}

Unfortunately for Jack, the [[House of High Magic]], a local [[mage]] guild, [[divination|divined]] that Jack's wildfire would bring some sort of magical calamity (possibly the [[Spellplague]]) to Ravens Bluff so they imprisoned Jack in magical stasis inside the mythal stone. He didn't escape until over a hundred years had passed.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|3122|9}}

The destruction of the wild mythal in the {{YearlinkName|1479}}, resulted in Jack losing his magical abilities.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|4960|13}}
